    {
      "type": "website",
      "html": "<div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content=\"\"><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Our studio is dedicated to providing holistic and enriching movement experiences that nurture the mind, body, and spirit. With a diverse range of classes led by experienced instructors, we invite you to explore the myriad paths of yoga, sculpting, and dance each tailored to meet your unique journey. Whether you're a seasoned yogi or just beginning to explore moving your body in new ways, our classes are designed to guide you toward a deeper connection with yourself, fostering self-love, mindfulness, and inner harmony. Step onto your mat and embark on a voyage of self-discovery and growth.</p></div>\n\n  \n</div></div>",
      "text": "Our studio is dedicated to providing holistic and enriching movement experiences that nurture the mind, body, and spirit. With a diverse range of classes led by experienced instructors, we invite you to explore the myriad paths of yoga, sculpting, and dance each tailored to meet your unique journey. Whether you're a seasoned yogi or just beginning to explore moving your body in new ways, our classes are designed to guide you toward a deeper connection with yourself, fostering self-love, mindfulness, and inner harmony. Step onto your mat and embark on a voyage of self-discovery and growth."
